---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro"
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Understand how Botyoo collects, uses, and protects your data across our Instagram automation services."
>
  <h1 class="text-foreground mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="mb-4"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 2025-05-08</p>

  <p class="mb-8">
    botyoo.com ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to
    protecting it through this Privacy Policy. This Policy explains what
    information we collect, how we use it, and your rights in relation to that
    data. It applies when you access or use our Instagram automation tool and
    related services ("Services").
  </p>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We collect the following categories of information:</p>

    <h3 class="text-foreground mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">a. Account & Profile Information</h3>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Name, email address, business name, social media handle(s), and password</li>
      <li>Information you provide when you register or contact support</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-foreground mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">b. Instagram/Meta Integration Data</h3>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Permissions granted via Instagram/Meta (access tokens, page IDs, DMs, comments, mentions, followers)</li>
      <li>Usage data related to automated actions</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-foreground mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">c. Usage & Technical Data</h3>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Device information, browser type, IP address, time zone</li>
      <li>Pages visited, time spent, crash logs</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>To operate and maintain our services</li>
      <li>To provide customer support and improve service quality</li>
      <li>To personalize user experience</li>
      <li>To monitor compliance with our terms and legal requirements</li>
      <li>To send important communications, including updates and notifications</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. Sharing Your Data</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">We may share data with:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Third-party services for analytics, hosting, and cloud storage</li>
      <li>Meta (Instagram) APIs based on the permissions you provide</li>
      <li>Legal authorities if required to comply with applicable law</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4"><strong>We never sell your personal data.</strong></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">4. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Depending on your location, you may have rights to:</p>
    <ul class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Access, modify, or delete your personal data</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      <li>Object to or restrict data processing</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">To exercise these rights, contact us at <strong class="text-foreground">hevin@botyoo.com</strong>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">We retain your information for as long as your account is active and for a reasonable period thereafter, or as required by law.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">6. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">We use encryption, access controls, and secure APIs to safeguard your information. However, no system is completely secure.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">botyoo.com is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">8. International Users</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">Your data may be processed and stored in the United States or other countries where we or our service providers operate.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">We may revise this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page and take effect upon publication.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">For questions or concerns, contact: <strong class="text-foreground">hevin@botyoo.com</strong></p>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>
